{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"0dd86a9f92","title":"在中共中央、中革军委负责人会议上的讲话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"370273bca4","index":0,"year":1935,"month":4,"day":28,"articleId":"0dd86a9f92"}],"tags":[{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"id":"e23dcf99fa","name":"发言","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji7-2","name":"毛泽东全集第7卷(2)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji7-2.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji7-2":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"88dfd28b21","type":"paragraph","text":"在中共中央、中革军委负责人","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"0dd86a9f92"},{"id":"13a776b102","type":"paragraph","text":"会议上的讲话","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"0dd86a9f92"},{"id":"04f00b5147","type":"paragraph","text":"（1935年4月28日）","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"0dd86a9f92"},{"id":"a1fb3abef6","type":"paragraph","text":"遵义会议后，我军大胆穿插，机动作战，把蒋介石的尾追部队甩在侧后，取得了北渡金沙江的有利时机。云南境内的地形条件，不像湖南、贵州有良好的山区可以利用，我军不宜在昆明东北平儿地带同敌人进行大的战斗。我军应沿江敌军空虚，尾追敌人距我尚有三四天的行程，迅速抢渡金沙江，以争取先机。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"0dd86a9f92"},{"id":"2602b233ac","type":"paragraph","text":"[1]1935年4月28日，毛泽东和朱德、周恩来等到鲁口哨、水平子一带宿营。当晚，出席中共中央、中革军委负责人会议，研究北渡金沙江的行动部署。这是毛泽东在会议上讲话的一部分。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"0dd86a9f92"}],"page":{"id":"1a5a26a2c4","publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"0dd86a9f92","start":169,"end":169}}}},"__N_SSG":true}